@startuml
title Master Data Management Flow

actor User
participant "UI: Master Data Tab" as UI
participant "API / Backend" as API
participant "Database" as DB

== Adding New Config ==
User -> UI: Select Category (e.g., Fragrances)
User -> UI: Enter New Type Text & Click Add
UI -> API: Submit New Type
API -> DB: Insert Record into Master Data Table
DB --> API: Success
API --> UI: Update UI List

== Archiving / Deleting Config (Soft Delete) ==
User -> UI: Click "Delete" on an item
UI -> API: Request Deletion (Item ID)

API -> DB: Check for Foreign Key references in Products Table
DB --> API: Return Usage Count

alt Item is In Use (Usage Count > 0)
    API -> DB: Soft Delete: Set isActive = false
    DB --> API: Success
    API --> UI: Item Archived (Hidden from new dropdowns)
    UI --> User: Show "Item Archived" Notification
else Item is NOT In Use (Usage Count == 0)
    API -> DB: Hard Delete Record from Master Data Table
    DB --> API: Success
    API --> UI: Item Removed Successfully
    UI --> User: Update UI List
end
@enduml
